- explain the whole system (MoCap,RespiTrace,video)
- explain quickly what we're going to do (stories)

- dressing :
    1/ jacket MoCap
    2/ respiration
        -> try different sizes
        -> explain how tu put it
        -> write down size (often 28f, 40 XXL)
        -> put the cables
    3/ bag for the respi
    4/ gloves MoCap
    5/ MoCap head
    6/ MoCap Rest
        right to left : shoulders, forearm, hands, back
        verify that all rigid bodies numbers correspond

- stretching with te arms to relax
- familiarisation : show how to bike with the hands, try with the legs
- start camera, MoCap, respi
- baseline : 2min respi, hands, legs

- show instructions
- try to be as expressive as you can be
- show introduction

for every story :
- explain the condition
- install all the possible things
- remember the person to be expressive (try to explain the shape etc)

*story*
- person comes in
* end of story*
